and the boundary.

00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:34.810
So the key thing is-- let me
write down the metric here,

00:00:34.810 --> 00:00:38.230
the Ads metric in this
Poincare coordinate.

00:00:46.420 --> 00:00:51.190
So this is the boundaries
are equal to zero.

00:00:51.190 --> 00:00:55.300
And when you increase
z, you go to interior.

00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:58.650
And then for each
constant, z, you

00:00:58.650 --> 00:01:01.240
have a Minkowski space time.

00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:02.880
You have a Minkowski d.

00:01:02.880 --> 00:01:06.670
So this is Ads d plus 1.

00:01:06.670 --> 00:01:11.520
So each slice is a d
dimension Minkowski space.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:16.230
And due to this redshift
factor, the more

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:20.610
you go to the interior
of the space time,

00:01:20.610 --> 00:01:22.390
then corresponding
to the lower energy

00:01:22.390 --> 00:01:24.750
process when viewed
form the field theory.

00:01:28.660 --> 00:01:32.280
So here, the same
process is happening here

00:01:32.280 --> 00:01:35.370
compared to happening here,
and here corresponding

00:01:35.370 --> 00:01:38.350
to the IR process, and
the [INAUDIBLE] boundary

00:01:38.350 --> 00:01:41.980
corresponding to the UV process.

00:01:41.980 --> 00:01:49.610
So this is a key
relation between the bulk

00:01:49.610 --> 00:01:51.500
and the boundary theories.

00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:54.480
And also, this gives you
an intuitive understanding

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:58.070
where does this actual dimension
come from from the field theory

00:01:58.070 --> 00:01:59.540
point of view.

00:01:59.540 --> 00:02:02.030
Then from the field
theory perspective,

00:02:02.030 --> 00:02:06.820
this actual dimension can be
considered as a geometrization

00:02:06.820 --> 00:02:10.720
of the energy scale.

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:14.260
And we know that the physics
change with the energy scale

00:02:14.260 --> 00:02:16.150
from the field
theory point of view.

00:02:16.150 --> 00:02:18.340
It's called the
normalization group flow,

00:02:18.340 --> 00:02:22.330
how physics evolves when you
change the energy or length

00:02:22.330 --> 00:02:23.320
scale.

00:02:23.320 --> 00:02:26.430
In the field theory, it's
called normalization group flow.

00:02:26.430 --> 00:02:31.610
So you can also view that the
evolution in the gravity side,

00:02:31.610 --> 00:02:35.320
say from the boundary
to the interior,

00:02:35.320 --> 00:02:38.670
and that this flow
in the z direction

00:02:38.670 --> 00:02:44.550
can be considered,
again, to geometrize

00:02:44.550 --> 00:02:46.753
the normalization group
flow of the field theory.

